---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<nav>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/notes/">Notes</a></li>
					<li><a href="/articles/">Articles</a></li>
					<li><a href="/audios/">Audios</a></li>
					<li><a href="/videos/">Videos</a></li>
					<li><a href="/projects/">Projects</a></li>
				</ul>
			</nav>

			<article>
				<h1><a href="/">{SITE_TITLE}'s Digital Space</a></h1>

				<p>Welcome! I'm Mayphus Tang, an innovator, creator, 
          and lifelong learner whose journey spans across multiple disciplines and interests. 
          My path has been shaped by an insatiable curiosity and a deep-seated desire to understand the world around us. 
          Through years of exploration and experimentation, I've cultivated a unique perspective that bridges technology, 
          nature, and human knowledge.</p>

				<p>As a technologist, I'm fascinated by the endless possibilities that emerge when we push the boundaries of what's possible. 
          My work often involves exploring cutting-edge technologies, from artificial intelligence to distributed systems, 
          always with an eye toward creating solutions that make a meaningful impact. Yet, my interests extend far beyond the digital realm.</p>

				<p>Nature has always been one of my greatest teachers.
          Whether I'm hiking through mountain trails or observing the intricate patterns in a leaf, 
          I find endless inspiration in the natural world. This connection to nature influences my approach to problem-solving and innovation, 
          reminding me that the most elegant solutions often mirror patterns found in the natural world.</p>

				<p>Knowledge, in all its forms, is what drives me forward.
          I believe in the power of continuous learning and the importance of sharing what we learn with others. 
          This space reflects my commitment to both personal growth and collective wisdom, serving as a platform where ideas can flourish and inspire.</p>

				<p>This website is a digital space where I cultivate my thoughts, ideas, and projects.
					It's a place for me to share my journey, learnings, and creations with the world.
					Here, you'll find a mix of contents.</p>
			</article>
		</main>
		<footer>
      <p>by Mayphus,
        last updated on
        {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { day: '2-digit', month: 'short', year: 'numeric' })}</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
  nav {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  nav ul {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  nav a:hover {
    color: white;
  }
</style>
